## Before / after snippet
**Bad (SRP violation)**
```java
class UserService {
  User find(String id){...}
  void email(User u){...} // wrong responsibility
}
```

**Better**
```java
class UserService {
  private final UserRepo repo;
  User find(String id){ return repo.find(id); }
}
class EmailNotifier { void send(User u){...} }
```

