## State + idempotency
```java
enum State { CREATED, PAID, CANCELLED, SHIPPED }
void onPaymentOk(String orderId, String payId){
  if (!orders.markPaidIf(orderId, State.CREATED, payId)) return; // idempotent
  inventory.reserve(orderId);
}
```

